      | stack_id | event_id | stack_name | logical_resource_id | resource_status | resource_type              | timestamp           |
      | 1        | 1        | vpc        | Vpc                 | CREATE_COMPLETE | AWS::EC2::VPC              | 2020-10-29 00:00:00 |
